{
  "texts": [
    "The model processed the answers and generated functional analysis based on the interactions.",
    "In each case study, we identified the exact contradiction that the TRIZ expert had considered in the source.",
    "Consequently, we selected that contradiction and utilized the model to generate ideas.",
    "The LLM API used in these three experiments was GPT 3.5, which was chosen for its robust capabilities and costeffectiveness, making it both accessible and convenient.",
    "In this study, we engaged evaluators to compare the output of our proposed model with the results of TRIZ experts."
  ]
}